nba <- read.csv("nba.csv", sep = ",", header = TRUE)
index <- nba$index
nba_ts <- ts(index,frequency = 12, start = 2004.000)
plot.ts(nba_ts)

twoyear <- nba$index[1:21]
twoyear_ts <- ts(twoyear,frequency = 12, start = 2004.000)
plot.ts(twoyear_ts)

t <- time(nba_ts)
model1 <- lm(nba_ts~t)
plot.ts(nba_ts)
abline(model1)

detrended <- resid(model1)
detrended_ts <- ts(detrended,frequency = 12, start = 2004.000)
adf.test(detrended_ts)
## Warning in adf.test(detrended_ts): p-value smaller than printed p-value
## 
##  Augmented Dickey-Fuller Test
## 
## data:  detrended_ts
## Dickey-Fuller = -5.1473, Lag order = 5, p-value = 0.01
## alternative hypothesis: stationary
plot.ts(detrended_ts)

plot(decompose(nba_ts))

training <- nba$index[1:169]
testing <- nba$index[170:181]
training_ts <- ts(training,frequency = 12, start = 2004.000)
plot.ts(training_ts)

t2 <- time(training_ts)
model2 <- lm(training_ts~t2)
training_detrended <- resid(model2)
training_detrended <- ts(training_detrended,frequency = 12, start = 2004.000)
training_detrended<-na.omit(training_detrended)
plot.ts(training_detrended)

Box.test(training_detrended, lag = 20, type = "Ljung-Box")
## 
##  Box-Ljung test
## 
## data:  training_detrended
## X-squared = 299.32, df = 20, p-value < 2.2e-16
adf.test(training_detrended)
## Warning in adf.test(training_detrended): p-value smaller than printed p-
## value
## 
##  Augmented Dickey-Fuller Test
## 
## data:  training_detrended
## Dickey-Fuller = -4.9028, Lag order = 5, p-value = 0.01
## alternative hypothesis: stationary
acf(training_detrended,lag=30)

pacf(training_detrended,lag=30)

raw_periodogram <- spec.pgram(training_detrended, taper=0, log="no")

df <- raw_periodogram$df
U <- qchisq(0.025,df)
L <- qchisq(0.975,df)
U
## [1] 0.03869307
L
## [1] 7.118033
smoothed_periodogram <- spec.pgram(training_detrended, taper=0, kernel('daniell',4),log="no")

z <- stl(training_detrended,"periodic")
training_rmsn <- z$time.series[,3]
plot.ts(training_rmsn)

raw_periodogram <- spec.pgram(training_rmsn, taper=0, log="no")

smoothed_periodogram <- spec.pgram(training_rmsn, taper=0, kernel('daniell',4),log="no")

df <- raw_periodogram$df
U <- qchisq(0.025,df)
L <- qchisq(0.975,df)
U
## [1] 0.03869307
L
## [1] 7.118033
acf(training_rmsn,lag=30)
